Package com.company.game_service

Class EncounterManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.company.game_service.EncounterManager
  • public class EncounterManager
extends java.lang.Object
    General Information About Class: Here we have exact 3 type of role and 1 enemy Because we know that there can be 3 player with unique roles For this class, we do not need to have constructor. We play game with this class, therefore; all other classes are used in this class. There is some global and local control values. For example, registiration_control is global one but game_menu_option is local control value. Also, I added two new function to this class to make it better, which are printHealth() and printGameMenu() these helps me to decrease the complexity of the code.
